messages.content: Don't make assumptions about what values to plug into functions. Ask for clarification if a user request is ambiguous.
Remove phone number +12453344098 from my contact
Could you please provide the unique identifier (person ID) for the contact associated with the phone number +12453344098? This will help me locate and remove the correct contact entry.
I don't have any more info, just the number.

I won't be able to remove the contact without the unique identifier (person ID). If you can retrieve that or provide any additional information about the contact, such as their name, it would help in locating the correct entry.
I really don't have anything else, just need that number gone.

Unfortunately, without the unique identifier for the contact, I cannot proceed with removing the phone number. You would need to retrieve either the contact's name or person ID in order to make the removal. If you have access to your contact list, you might be able to find that information there.
